{"tid":1263924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(海濱送中)中環解放軍碼頭出生過程同背景","createTime":"2019-06-28T12:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T00:23:00.000Z","uid":260929,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d007ca644d9c4152ff7185e508123d6bbb406a","tid":1263924,"uid":260929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"主要講行動嘅post,大家可以去返嗰面集中傾<br />\n［好L興奮］中環今晚凌晨割比解放軍！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1263351/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1263351/page/1</a><br />\n【重要】去中環海濱前一定要睇！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1263893/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1263893/page/1</a><br />\n今晚收工想去中環海濱集會，但係有個好重要嘅問題想問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1263708/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1263708/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才整合咗啲資料, 等大家可以了解吓成件事點蒞<br />\n同埋個人認為反對都要有原因,唔好好似啲廢中廢老咁問多兩問就死曬,講嘢亳無邏輯<br />\n今次呢單嘢,地其實唔多,嗰啲咩土地供應嘅嘢就唔講啦(大家都心中有數要點講),主要攞返啲陳年論點出蒞(係呀,當年有人提過,但政府無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dAm9JFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdAm9JFJ.png&h=a4dedf64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bgtZd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bgtZd3.png&h=f5c65e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30i4xy4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30i4xy4.png&h=6dbcb3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望有少少用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e1f06e57be53aab1ac5e04e60199c219b4f882","tid":1263924,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"熱愛香港嘅各位，麻煩一人申請多一個Facebook帳號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263600</a>"},{"pid":"6858a70287db4d96bd72242718ff82a865323a23","tid":1263924,"uid"