Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F1303861012%2F0&h=7a016ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片"},{"pid":"e1be35d684b64a0842a5fe0226acc195192bb2ac","tid":1263924,"uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"50a09643a13840b307fb775db2425ee01de84173","tid":1263924,"uid":99883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦，搞到跑步都唔可以沿維港邊跑，呢個撚屌碼頭阻撚住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544f054f08c213bbf123ebdb08819a63e4884790","tid":1263924,"uid":250036,"like":12,"dislike":24,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"順便八卦一問，想知呢度既90後00後知唔知政府總部廿年前係一個港口?<br />\n<br />\n(純粹想知我既generation同大家既認知差距有幾大)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知"},{"pid":"15e14f1ef11b6f6b18b0f98052d365498e83550b","tid":1263924,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"司法覆核進度點"},{"pid":"fe76221c8c6e4d9e59dd084fcf261867f86dc7c9","tid":1263924,"uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fde0317f5e26cc4f106d77996a68ba2ba3f8e0a","tid":1263924,"uid":260929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"好對唔住,有個位check漏咗,創建香港原來已經退出咗司法覆核(因為無錢),所以政府今年先可以正式申請移交<br />\n城規會撥地建解放軍碼頭遭覆核 何來申加入訴訟被拒(2018年11月30日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3696027-城規會撥地建解放軍碼頭遭覆核-何來申加入訴訟被\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F3696027-%E5%9F%8E%E8%A6%8F%E6%9C%83%E6%92%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%BA%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E9%81%AD%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8-%E4%BD%95%E4%BE%86%E7%94%B3%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E8%A2%AB&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2Fewiyebc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=3e3cbbfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3696027-城規會撥地建解放軍碼頭遭覆核-何來申加入訴訟被</a><br />\n而家只有岑敖暉4月入紙司法覆核,詳情我都唔清楚,但好明顯已經無得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v630Rn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv630Rn7.png&h=70878f08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e6c6909884ea5c4539454914bdc3229563025e1","tid":1263924,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"0d76bd611b008cba63b2934ed9836dd61029e460","tid":1263924,"uid":7902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"咁2007年政府嘅回應 係咪出爾反爾？"},{"pid":"ce9bf5c5aa6828de53fbc9415dec0a13f3e107d3","tid":1263924,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"支持解放軍武力清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5a8ddd0204f239dae6923d2c80bc349d26ecf6","tid":1263924,"uid":8745,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuTL3dQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuTL3dQ.jpg&h=cf971243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得點解中環維港要起個軍事碼頭？又係支那殖民宗主國要攞彩囉<br />\n支那要透過摧毀前殖民者個套，自己整個更大更靚嘅，證明自己威過前宗主國英國，個種殖民者嘅嘴臉出晒黎<br />\n<br />\n大家可以留意返皇后碼頭原來嘅位置係愛丁堡廣場出面（龍和道）<br />\n歷來英女皇同港督都係度搭船上岸，隔離就係軍營，2006年同你拆左呢個英殖象徵，係隔離幫解放軍起個大d新d嘅，當年中英有呢個deal都唔出奇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2006年拆卸皇后碼頭，都係由林鄭主理</span></strong>"},{"pid":"636798c2e57661d2d73d2ef0b27094b30a6da016","tid":1263924,"uid":23916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}